5
00:00:16,540 --> 00:00:17,510
She'll come tomorrow morning.

6
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:18,910
Maid?

7
00:00:20,100 --> 00:00:21,430
She can help you with housework

8
00:00:21,440 --> 00:00:22,470
and cooking.

9
00:00:22,880 --> 00:00:24,590
Most importantly,
she can keep you company.

10
00:00:24,770 --> 00:00:26,350
I don't want you to feel lonely at home.

11
00:00:26,600 --> 00:00:27,440
Thanks, honey.

12
00:00:28,390 --> 00:00:29,230
Let's go to sleep.

13
