91
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:51,600
Honey.

92
00:04:52,760 --> 00:04:53,790
You must be tired.

93
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:54,760
I'm exhausted.

94
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:55,790
I'll get some sleep.

95
00:04:55,840 --> 00:04:57,270
It's okay.

